{"tid":1592851,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"咁樣你地都相信荃灣死者係自殺","createTime":"2019-09-24T20:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T22:15:38.000Z","uid":80936,"like":108,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"a8df97145ee4a6e93c9c968bb006f3fddb0b10b6","tid":1592851,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T20:34:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/egMVzPq.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FegMVzPq.jpg&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=188ca965\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/egMVzPq.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n大大張膠紙黐喺個嘴到<br />\n都可以有一大堆人話係炒車<br />\n我都唔知有乜嘢好講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪想同我講佢自殺之前<br />\n用膠紙黐係自己個嘴度啊？<br />\n<br />\n定係想同我講撈上嚟之後<br />\n班狗先再用膠紙黐喺死者個嘴度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋點解佢俾人告緊<br />\n就代表佢係畏罪自殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先唔講個家屬係咪真啦<br />\n死者屋企人話佢冇出過去發夢啫<br />\n但咁就代表佢真係冇出去啦咩？<br />\n<br />\n大把人出去發夢都唔會屋企人講㗎<br />\n因為政見唔同啊嘛<br />\n<br />\n唔講死者嘅姿勢<br />\n咁頭上面嘅傷口呢？<br />\n<br />\n屍體發現預告呢？<br />\n<br />\n根本一大堆疑點都指同一點<br />\n就係<span style=\"color: red;\">佢點都唔係自殺</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家嘅香港<br />\n已經唔再係以前嘅香港<br />\n<br />\n就好似警察<br />\n都已經唔再係除暴安良嘅存在</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">面對現實啦香港人</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9139e26ac69848aaa1cda73d1ba497f419c5d7c9","tid":1592851,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T20:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"31d9f2eca324c016d