個鼻去吸入海水咁死。<br />\n<br />\n三、<span style=\"color: red;\">各大網絡討論已預言將會發現屍體，略計算急凍與海水既溶雪時間、地點完全吻合一條被解凍既屍體</span><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再推炒車post"},{"pid":"a5150b87655c34e9c2a8925b70ec25c93b5e9bfb","tid":1592851,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請留意5毛風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"3940aa22cc70101cd038990c885762db4933ee23","tid":1592851,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29ea4f367d3e96f310e6782f658f0358ea057c76","tid":1592851,"uid":34047,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T20:44:48.000Z","msg":"認同樓主<br />\n個膠紙同啲傷<br />\n再睇返女朋友同屋企人既反應<br />\n正常見到自己男友或者仔既遺體咁樣<br />\n就算當事人有講過自殺都好<br />\n家人見到都一定會覺得有可疑<br />\n但佢地反而係第一時間同人講無可疑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"唔係唔理 只係而家主要係之後嘅行動 反赤納粹 做好對外文宣<br />\n<br />\n仲有邊有人查案會日日大大聲叫 我查緊你呀 你因住呀"},{"pid":"ff8712be5142c02db9cc33856e266eb34ac9ab2c","tid":1592851,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:04:31.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"31f151343097acb0258751243cdf9f4e0c17fe40","tid":1592851,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"好多人叫人唔好查<br />\n是但搵個「家屬」就話炒車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警你當香港人on鳩？"},{"pid":"cb869d2b973b734ff4b08ec973887f015b17a6c0","tid":1592851,"uid":245394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:19:05.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"470d9ffb2eb71135c33b0846bfbf7e40f7f788b0","tid":1592851,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:27:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcfd635b0ac9f22841a23089cdca45fac13fb7a7","tid":1592851,"uid":30582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:43:43.000Z","msg":"屍體唔會講大話。我都係相信疑點太多了